  <scopecontent id="aspace_af1cf0691fec2f8521987a47bd464d24">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Letters relating chiefly to the sale, leasing, and development of land, to lumbering, and to political and social life in Chenango County, New York. Correspondents include Colonel Cady, Obadiah German, Abraham R. Lawrence, Caleb Lawrence, W.T. Lawrence, Robert L. Livingston, Theodore Sill, John Sudam, Simon G. Throop, Gerrit Van Wagenen, and Marinus Willett.</p>  </scopecontent>
